          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Military Recruiter Right to Carry Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill states that, notwithstanding any Department of Defense policy or federal, state, or local law to the contrary, a member of the Armed Forces assigned to duty at an Armed Forces recruitment office has the right to carry a personal or service-issue firearm at the office.</p>]]></text>
